name: HEN Sol
description: This image is of our sun 'Sol' taken on the 13/6/2014 and has the iconic Hic et nunc logo projected on to it. The image was taken and processed by myself and shows numerous, unique sunspot AR regions. HEN Sol captures a unique glimpse to the past as well as offering a cool piece of art for Hic et nunc enthusiasts. The dimensions of this image are 2472 x 2496
